## Additional Safety Disclaimer

This software is designed to assist in monitoring LPG (Liquefied Petroleum Gas) 
systems but should never replace proper safety procedures, professional 
inspections, or adherence to local safety regulations.

IMPORTANT SAFETY NOTICE:
- Always follow manufacturer guidelines for LPG equipment
- Regular professional inspections are required regardless of this system
- This system is not certified for safety-critical applications
- Users assume full responsibility for proper installation and usage
- Emergency response procedures should not rely solely on this system
- Comply with all local building codes and safety regulations

The developers and contributors of this project disclaim any liability for 
property damage, personal injury, or loss of life resulting from the use or 
misuse of this software and associated hardware.